metadata.description:
In 2013, my album OUT OF THE BLACK was released. 
In celebration of 10 years, I am releasing this unreleased song „Vocode“. 

„Vocode“ was a track I made during the „Out Of The Black“ album process, you can hear similarities to „Rocky 2“ or „Touch It“ and it’s got that banging vibe from my classic „& Down“. 
I played it out in clubs in the early 10’s, but decided not to include it in the album. If you love the hard & funky sound from that time, here’s something special from the vaults that would have been lost to history. 
Artwork by Yoshiro Nishi.
metadata.name: "Vocode" #1
